## Summary

This documentation covers the Amplitude Guides and Surveys Web SDK implementation, including installation methods (Amplitude Browser SDK plugin, standalone with third-party analytics, Google Tag Manager), initialization with `init()` and `boot()` methods, user/session property management, and integration patterns for SPAs and desktop frameworks like Electron.

